      I repeat, emergency.
 - Oh, my God, he's been shot!

12:04.424 --> 12:06.024
- I need an ambulance
at my current location.

12:06.026 --> 12:07.425
We have a gunshot wound victim.

12:07.427 --> 12:09.294
Get me that ambulance now!

