       - GSW to the neck.

12:21.508 --> 12:24.209
   GCS 3, tubed in the ambo.

12:24.211 --> 12:26.077
   Pupils fixed and dilated?
             - Yup.

12:26.079 --> 12:27.345
 - Sinus tachy on the monitor.

