   He was bound in the trunk
           of a car.

12:28.949 --> 12:29.948
           - Rotate.

12:29.950 --> 12:31.883
         <i>[dramatic music]</i>

12:31.885 --> 12:33.384
     Get ready to transfer.

12:33.386 --> 12:35.820
            - Ready?
   Three, two, one--transfer.

12:35.822 --> 12:37.055
  - Hank, let's step outside.

12:37.057 --> 12:38.056
- Is he breathing?

12:38.058 --> 12:39.224
      - I need a CT head.

12:39.226 --> 12:40.425
   Someone call neurosurgery!

12:40.427 --> 12:41.426
- Is he still breathing?

12:41.428 --> 12:43.895
  - Checking right now, Hank.

12:43.897 --> 12:45.130
           - Come on,
     let them do their job.

12:45.132 --> 12:47.999
         - Oh, my God!
      - Get me a head CT.

12:48.001 --> 12:50.135
               <i>â™ª </i>

